OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,FA man has been spared jail after
OL,7,Fkilling a young couple who were headed
OL,8,Fon holiday in a crash.
OL,10,FAlexander MacCallum, 28, previously
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to causing the deaths
OL,12,Fof Katie Worrell, 25, and Adam
OL,13,FMuskett, 27, by careless driving.
OL,15,FSwansea Crown Court heard that Miss
OL,16,FWorrell and Mr Muskett were a couple
OL,17,Fand had been travelling on holiday to
OL,18,Fcelebrate Ms Worrell's birthday
OL,19,Ftogether.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,FHidden in the car were balloons,
OL,7,Fbanners and presents which Mr Muskett
OL,8,Fhad brought to surprise his
OL,9,Fgirlfriend, the court heard.
OL,11,FOn Thursday (2 April), Judge Paul
OL,12,FThomas KC gave MacCallum a suspended
OL,13,Fsentence and disqualified him from
OL,14,Fdriving for 18 months.
OL,16,FMiss Worrell, from Pembroke, and Mr
OL,17,FMuskett, from Tenby, died after
OL,18,FMacCallum's Jaguar XKR hit the Ford
OL,19,FFiesta they were travelling in on the
OL,20,FA477 in Carmarthenshire on 13 June
OL,21,F2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court heard the driving
OL,7,Fconditions were very poor at the time
OL,8,Fof the crash due to heavy rain.
OL,10,FCraig Jones, prosecuting, said the two
OL,11,Fvehicles had been travelling in
OL,12,Fopposite directions but witnesses
OL,13,Freported seeing MacCallum's Jaguar
OL,14,F"travelling at speed in the heavy
OL,15,Frain" and overtaking another vehicle
OL,16,Fshortly before the collision.
OL,18,FMr Jones said MacCallum lost control
OL,19,Fof his vehicle when it entered the
OL,20,Fopposite lane and hit the Ford Fiesta
OL,21,Fcarrying Ms Worrell and Mr Muskett.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@EO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,FFollowing the crash, MacCallum told a
OL,7,Fwitness: "I was overtaking, put my
OL,8,Ffoot down, and lost it in the wet."
OL,10,FMacCallum is believed to have been
OL,11,Fdriving at the 60mph speed limit at
OL,12,Fthe time of the collision, but was
OL,13,Ftravelling inappropriately fast for
OL,14,Fthe "horrendous" weather conditions,
OL,15,FMr Jones told the court.
OL,17,FMr Jones said: "Both Adam and Katie
OL,18,Fsustained injuries during the course
OL,19,Fof the collision, which sadly proved
OL,20,Funsurvivable.
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@cO]vD@EOUvD@PO]yD@POU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,F"Tragically, Mr Muskett died at the
OL,7,Fscene and Miss Worrell passed away at
OL,8,Fhospital."
OL,10,FMartyn Hynes, defending, described
OL,11,FMacCallum's actions as a "fatal error
OL,12,Fin judgment" and said the defendant
OL,13,Fshowed genuine remorse for the deaths
OL,14,Fof Miss Worrell and Mr Muskett.
OL,16,F"There is a full realisation and
OL,17,Facceptance by the defendant that he is
OL,18,Fresponsible," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]sD@ZOUtD@LO]xD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,F"It was a momentary lapse (in
OL,7,Fjudgment) as opposed to deliberate and
OL,8,Fsustained bad driving."
OL,10,FMacCallum was given a 16-month prison
OL,11,Fsentence, suspended for 12 months,
OL,12,Fordered to carry out 200 hours of
OL,13,Funpaid work in the community and
OL,14,Fdisqualified from driving for 18
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,FSentencing MacCallum, Judge Thomas
OL,18,Fsaid: "This terrible event, nearly two
OL,19,Fyears ago, lasted for a matter of
OL,20,Fseconds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]zD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,F"But it caused the utterly tragic
OL,7,Fdeath of two lovely young people, with
OL,8,Ftheir lives so full of promise."
OL,10,FJudge Thomas said, while the speed
OL,11,Flimit was not exceeded, MacCallum's
OL,12,Fdriving was "simply not appropriate"
OL,13,Fdue to the heavy rain.
OL,15,F"You put your foot down when your
OL,16,Fvision was limited in horrendous
OL,17,Fdriving conditions," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]tD@MOUtD@dO]wD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
