OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1775426988
OL,3,CDriver spared jail sentence over
OL,4,Ckilling of young couple in crash
OL,6,FHe said he understood the families of
OL,7,Fthe victims would like him to "throw
OL,8,Faway the key," but stressed he was
OL,9,Flimited in the sentence he could
OL,10,Fimpose.
OL,12,FHe added that MacCallum had no
OL,13,Fprevious convictions and was of
OL,14,F"general excellent character".
OL,16,F"You are genuinely aware of the
OL,17,Fdevastation, of the impact of what you
OL,18,Fhave done," he told MacCallum.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@NO]vD@AOUvD@]O]xD@AOUzD@KO]
